OL,3,CRebranded Planning Minister role could
OL,4,Cput environment at risk, say
OL,5,Ccampaigners
OL,7,FEnvironmental campaigners in Jersey
OL,8,Ffear the island's green spaces could
OL,9,Fbe at risk due to the creation of a
OL,10,Fnew ministerial role in government.
OL,12,FSenator Sir Mark Boleat was appointed
OL,13,FMinister for Planning and Regulation
OL,14,Fin the States today.
OL,16,FThe position no longer contains a
OL,17,Fportfolio for the environment, which
OL,18,Fcritics believe may threaten Jersey's
OL,19,Frural areas.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/5
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
