PN,35102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1784060308
OL,3,CRebranded Planning Minister role could
OL,4,Cput environment at risk, say
OL,5,Ccampaigners
OL,7,FAndrew Le Quesne, a campaigner, told
OL,8,FITV News: "In extremis, we build
OL,9,Feverywhere and we end up looking like
OL,10,FHong Kong and I don't think anyone who
OL,11,Flives here wants that.
OL,13,F"A lot of people I've spoken to
OL,14,Fgenuinely believe this is almost an
OL,15,Fexercise in sleight of hand and there
OL,16,Fare a lot more green fields and a lot
OL,17,Fmore open spaces that are going to be
OL,18,Fat risk."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/5
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1784060308
OL,3,CRebranded Planning Minister role could
OL,4,Cput environment at risk, say
OL,5,Ccampaigners
OL,7,FHowever, some construction firms have
OL,8,Fwelcomed the separation of planning
OL,9,Fand environmental responsibilities,
OL,10,Fsaying it could help tackle the
OL,11,Fisland's housing crisis.
OL,13,FBen Cairney, manager of a construction
OL,14,Fbusiness, says: "The driving factor
OL,15,Fbehind the cost of housing is how much
OL,16,Fit actually costs to build homes and a
OL,17,Flot of that comes down to time. You've
OL,18,Fheard the phrase 'time is money',
OL,19,Fwell, the longer things take, the more
OL,20,Fit's going to cost.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/5
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1784060308
OL,3,CRebranded Planning Minister role could
OL,4,Cput environment at risk, say
OL,5,Ccampaigners
OL,7,F"Anything we can do to reduce the time
OL,8,Fit takes to get something from
OL,9,Fconcept, through planning, to being
OL,10,Ffinished, would reduce that cost."
OL,12,FAnd while Senator Boleat faced
OL,13,Fquestions from fellow States members
OL,14,Fabout what the rebadged ministerial
OL,15,Frole will mean, he told ITV News that
OL,16,Fthe change will have no "adverse
OL,17,Feffect" on the environment.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/5
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1784060308
OL,3,CRebranded Planning Minister role could
OL,4,Cput environment at risk, say
OL,5,Ccampaigners
OL,7,FSenator Boleat says: "It's about doing
OL,8,Fit properly. We over-regulate in this
OL,9,Fisland. I think there's common
OL,10,Fagreement on that.
OL,12,F"There's scope for us to cut
OL,13,Fregulation that will not have any
OL,14,Fadverse effect on the environment or
OL,15,Fpeople's safety."
OL,17,FITV News also understands that some of
OL,18,Fthe human and financial resources
OL,19,Fformerly dedicated to the Government's
OL,20,Fenvironment portfolio will be
OL,21,Ftransferred to the planning department.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/5
